tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE warehouse_performance_metrics (
    warehouse_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    total_sales DECIMAL,
    total_shipments INT,
    warehouse_size INT
);

CREATE TABLE warehouse_performance_metrics (
  warehouse_id INT,
  metric_date DATE,
  revenue DECIMAL,
  expenses DECIMAL,
  profit DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE warehouse_sales_metrics (
  warehouse_id INT,
  metric_date DATE,
  orders_count INT,
  average_order_value DECIMAL,
  sales_total DECIMAL
);
